    "description": "Are you a skilled Full Stack Developer looking for your next big career move? ISRO Advisory Limited in Ghaziabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout ISRO Advisory Limited:\nISRO Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ISRO Advisory Limited!",
